quotes.text: While you're sleeping, someone else is coding their way into FAANG.
quotes.author: Unknown

quotes.text: Every LeetCode problem you skip is another candidate getting ahead of you.
quotes.author: Unknown

quotes.text: If you fail, remember—someone dumber than you is getting that FAANG offer right now.
quotes.author: Unknown

quotes.text: Your excuses won’t get you an offer. Your consistency will.
quotes.author: Unknown

quotes.text: Do you want to be rich or do you want to be comfortable? Choose wisely.
quotes.author: Unknown

quotes.text: FAANG isn’t for the weak. If you can’t handle the grind, step aside.
quotes.author: Unknown

quotes.text: Your friends are chilling. You? You’ll be negotiating FAANG salaries soon.
quotes.author: Unknown

quotes.text: Your competition is studying right now. What’s your excuse?
quotes.author: Unknown

quotes.text: They say it’s impossible. Good. That means fewer people are competing with you.
quotes.author: Unknown

quotes.text: If it was easy, everyone would do it. Be the outlier.
quotes.author: Unknown
